&lt;Telematics InternationalInc> said 2,550,000 shares of common at 12 dlrs per share arebeing offered in an initial public offering.    It said it is offering 2,050,000 and certain shareholdersare offering 500,000 shares.    &lt;Alex. Brown and Sons Inc> and Robertson, Colman andStephens are the managers of the syndicate offering the largernumber of shares, and Alex. Brown, Colman and Hambros BankLimited are the managers of the international offering of500,000 shares. Reuter&#3;